
## Screenshots

Here are example outputs from running the project using `sample_data.csv`:

### 1️⃣ Bar Chart of Numeric Columns
![Bar Chart](screenshots/bar_chart.png)
> Shows the numeric columns (`Age`, `Score`, `Hours_Studied`) for each row in a bar chart.

### 2️⃣ Histograms of Numeric Columns
![Histogram](screenshots/histogram.png)
> Displays the distribution of values for each numeric column in the dataset.

### 3️⃣ Summary Statistics
![Summary Statistics](screenshots/summary.png)
> Shows descriptive statistics such as mean, min, max, and standard deviation for numeric columns.
